OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774023076
OL,3,CHealthcare charities save government
OL,4,Cmillions every year in Jersey
OL,6,FJersey relies more heavily on
OL,7,Fcharities to deliver health and social
OL,8,Fcare services than other jurisdictions
OL,9,Fdo, according to a director at the
OL,10,Fisland's Community Foundation.
OL,12,FRosemarie Finley's comments come after
OL,13,Fa report published by the Community
OL,14,FFoundation today (18 March) found
OL,15,Fhealth and care charities delivered
OL,16,Faround #6.2 million in net savings for
OL,17,Fthe government in 2024.
OL,19,FIt further found these charities
OL,20,Fgenerated an estimated #137.4 million
OL,21,Fin economic and social value.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
