FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774023076
OL,3,CHealthcare charities save government
OL,4,Cmillions every year in Jersey
OL,6,FThe report - which investigated the
OL,7,Fwork of 13 local health, social care,
OL,8,Fand wellbeing charities - aimed to
OL,9,Fmeasure the impact of the third sector
OL,10,Fand identify ways that their services
OL,11,Fcould be delivered more effectively.
OL,13,FThe Community Foundation argues its
OL,14,Ffindings highlight the critical role
OL,15,Flocal healthcare charities play in
OL,16,Fsupporting islanders and reducing
OL,17,Fpressures on public services such as
OL,18,Fthe hospital.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
