OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774023076
OL,3,CHealthcare charities save government
OL,4,Cmillions every year in Jersey
OL,6,FRosemarie told ITV News the report
OL,7,Fhighlights "how important early
OL,8,Fintervention and prevention is" when
OL,9,Fit comes to healthcare outcomes.
OL,11,F"The difficulty is that currently we
OL,12,Fonly spend about 6% of the health
OL,13,Fbudget on early intervention and
OL,14,Fprevention, and it needs to be more",
OL,15,Fshe explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774023076
OL,3,CHealthcare charities save government
OL,4,Cmillions every year in Jersey
OL,6,FRosemarie adds that the 13 charities
OL,7,Finvestigated - such as Brighter
OL,8,FFutures, Family Nursing and Home Care,
OL,9,FMind Jersey, Every Child our Future,
OL,10,Fand Enable - are particularly skilled
OL,11,Fat delivering preventative healthcare
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,F"They're an important part of the
OL,15,Fhealth economy here in Jersey", she
OL,16,Fexplains, "and this piece of work was
OL,17,Fabout looking at how beneficial those
OL,18,Fcharities are (and demonstrates their
OL,19,Fvalue for money)."
OL,26,@zD@Opm{D@Ppn
