PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774023076
OL,3,CHealthcare charities save government
OL,4,Cmillions every year in Jersey
OL,6,FRosemarie explains that this is a
OL,7,Fparticularly unique system, as "some
OL,8,Fof the work that charities do here in
OL,9,FJersey would be done by governments
OL,10,Felsewhere".
OL,12,FWhilst she says this is not
OL,13,Fnecessarily a bad thing - as charities
OL,14,Fdeliver their services well - work
OL,15,Fneeds to be done to ensure the
OL,16,Flongevity of this dependence upon the
OL,17,Fthird sector going forwards.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
