CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1774023076
OL,3,CHealthcare charities save government
OL,4,Cmillions every year in Jersey
OL,6,FThese include things such as
OL,7,Festablishing clear lines of
OL,8,Fcommunication with government,
OL,9,Fdeveloping long-term funding models
OL,10,Ffor charities delivering essential
OL,11,Fservices, and collaborating more
OL,12,Fbetween different charities on
OL,13,Ftackling big problems.
OL,15,F"Health and the needs and requirements
OL,16,Ffor health in Jersey are growing",
OL,17,FRosemarie says.
OL,19,F"We know that in the years between
OL,20,F2023 and 2043, GP visits will increase
OL,21,Fby about 11 percent.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
